    {
      "$id": 1,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0010",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Guu[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 2,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0020",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "The power of the cores is[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 3,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0030",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Guoooooh[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 4,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0040",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "The Ares?![ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 5,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0050",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Al![ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 6,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0060",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I will never understand it[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 7,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0070",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "If my limit is my inability to accept it[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 8,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0080",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I will swallow you as many times as it takes[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 9,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0090",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Until you become the very root of myself[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 10,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0100",
      "style": 0,
      "name": ""
    },
    {
      "$id": 11,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0110",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Try it[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 12,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0120",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "To someone like you who exists[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 13,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0130",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "without any meaning[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 14,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0140",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Do you really think you\ncan swallow my emotion[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 15,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0150",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "that strives to live?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 16,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG9010",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "It's \"will.\" The strong\nwill and impulse to live[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 17,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG9030",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "In other words, \"love.\"[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 18,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG9035",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Do you have the resolve to love? It's not\nlike exchanging wedding vows, you know.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 19,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG9040",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "It is the \"love\" to love everything in\nthis world[ST:wide ]— the entire world itself.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 20,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG9050",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Until you have that resolve, I\ncannot hand the Ares over to you.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 21,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0210",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "This is by no means understanding.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 22,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0220",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Nor is it acceptance.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 23,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0230",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "It is extermination through assimilation[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 24,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0240",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "A culling of intellect![ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 25,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0250",
      "style": 0,
      "name": ""
    },
    {
      "$id": 26,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0260",
      "style": 0,
      "name": ""
    },
    {
      "$id": 27,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0270",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "It's okay.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 28,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0280",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "\"I am with you.\"[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 29,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0290",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "You can do this, right?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 30,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0300",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "The Ares is[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 31,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0310",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "receiving human consciousness[ST:wide ]—?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 32,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0320",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "It's just like the Vita.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 33,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0330",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "The Vita was a receptacle\nfor Void alone, but[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 34,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0340",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "The Ares[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 35,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0350",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "is serving as a receptacle\nfor all of humanity![ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 36,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0360",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Is this[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 37,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0370",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "what flows out from the abyss[ST:wide ]—!?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 38,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0380",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "They watched over me as I departed[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 39,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0390",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "My comrades from my distant homeworld[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 40,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0400",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Yeah.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 41,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0410",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I know.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 42,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0420",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Leon[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 43,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0430",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Yeah, leave it to me.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 44,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0450",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Lin[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 45,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0485",
      "style": 0,
      "name": ""
    },
    {
      "$id": 46,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0460",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Thanks to you, my life had meaning too[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 47,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0470",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I wanted to thank you.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 48,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0480",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Lao[ST:wide ]—san[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 49,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0490",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I'll lend you my strength too.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 50,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0500",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Yo, Mr. Hero.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 51,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0510",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "You were talking big back\nthere, so what happened?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 52,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG9060",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I haven't finished protecting the\nthings I want to protect yet.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 53,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG9070",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Leaving behind unresolved feelings\nand saying goodbye all by myself[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 54,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG9080",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I'll pass on that.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 55,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0550",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Shut up.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 56,
      "label": "xs33810100_MSG0560",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Did you come back as a\nghost just to say that?[ST:wait ]"
    },
